The Dark Hordes - changelog
---------------------------

Version 0.8.2
- General:
    * Deleted the 'dist' folder after it had served its purpose completely
    * Prepared menu.cfg for each part (modified _main.cfg)
    * Changed the extensions of some documents and moved them to the 'notes' folder
- Scenarios:
    * Turns and gold readjusted in all scenarios
    * 01 - A New Chance
        + Added new loyal character Corcyn who appears along the way
        + One more enemy leader added
        + Some dialogs added
    * 03 - Skull of Morgorath
        + Changed so that all orcish warlords are allied
        + Some dialogs added
        + Randomized the owner of the skull (to prevent cheating)
    * 05 - Inside the Tower
        + Two villages established
        + Enemy reinforcements added to appear every few turns
    * 06 - Crelanus Book
        + The map changed significantly
        + Added bonus for defeating elven leaders
    * 07 - Confrontation
        + The map changed significantly (to reduce the difficulty)
    * 08 - Underground Pool
        + The map changed significantly (to eliminate bottlenecks)
        + Some dialogs added
    * 09 - Underground River
        + The objectives were very confusing and therefore corrected
        + Reworked map slightly
- Translations:
    * Additional Japanese translation provided
    * POT included in package
- Units:
    * Added undead traits to Gwiti
- Utils
    * Added and optimized several macros
- Achievements:
    * Newly added (currently there is only one, to be expanded sequentially)

Version 0.8.0
- General:
    * Campaign updated for 1.18
    * Directory structure changed drastically
    * Thoroughly fixed bugs and glitches
- Music:
    * Added heavens-remix.ogg
    * Added wesnoth-3.ogg
- Graphics & Artwork:
    * New recolors for Dark Initiate and Dread Lich
- Scenarios:
    * Outdated or poor elements removed from all scenarios and maps
    * Maps reworked in modern style
    * Gold for all scenarios adjusted, difficulty increased slightly
    * 01 - A New Chance
        + Difficulty increased slightly
        + Gwiti's dialogue added as minimum required
    * 03 - Skull of Morgorath
        + All orcish leaders became Warlords
        + Leganoth now with loyal traits
    * 06 - Crelanus Book
        + Enemies can no longer recruit zombies
    * 07 - Confrontation
        + The map changed significantly, difficulty reduced
        + Tanar's traits changed to quick
    * 10 - Return to the Northlands
       + Gwiti to be Demilich at the start of part 2
       + Significant bug fixes
    * 11 - An Orcish Coup
       + Map completed
       + Gold and income received adjustments to reduce difficulty
    * 12 - Assault on Alduin (NEW)
- Units:
    * Initiate renamed to Dark Initiate
    * New unit Dark Acolyte added. Gwiti can no longer be lich by mere advances
        + Lv1 Dark Initiate => Lv2 Dark Acolyte => Lv3 Deathmaster
        + Lv3 Demilich => Lv4 Dread Lich
    * Fine-tuning of moves and hitpoints for all units
- Misc:
   * Other improvements too numerous to mention here

Version 0.7.1+svn
- Translations from Wescamp
    * Updated translations: ga, nl, possibly others

Version 0.7.1
- General:
    * Campaign updated for 1.10
- Translations from Wescamp
    * New translations: ga, sr@ijekavian, sr@ijekavianlatin
    * Updated translations: (almost) all of the others
- Units
    * Dread Lich adapted to new AMLA XP standard of 50 XP/level

Version 0.7.0
- General
